# No AI MDC File Edits

Rule to prevent AI from modifying Cursor rule files.

<rule>
name: no-ai-mdc-edits
description: Prevent AI from modifying .mdc files
filters:
  - type: file_extension
    pattern: "\\.mdc$"
  - type: event
    pattern: "file_modify"
actions:
  - type: reject
    message: "AI cannot modify .mdc files. These files can only be modified by the user."
examples:
  - input: "AI attempting to edit .mdc file"
    output: "Rejected: AI cannot modify .mdc files"
metadata:
  priority: high
  version: 1.0
</rule>